Program: Last Word
Title: Masha Leon, Tim Pigott-Smith, Christopher Morahan, Parv Bancil, Marthe Gosteli, Brian Matthew
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b08lk540
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 16 Apr 2017
Julian Worricker on: The society columnist and Holocaust survivor, Masha Leon.... Actor Tim Pigott-Smith and director Christopher Morahan, who worked together on ITV's The Jewel in the Crown.... Playwright Parv Bancil whose work tackled issues affecting young British Asians.... Marthe Gosteli, who was at the forefront of the campaign to get women the vote in Switzerland.... And the broadcaster, host of 'Sounds of the Sixties', Brian Matthew. Show less